ZH: 地质学是研究地球内部结构和成分的学科。
EN: Geology is the study of the structure and composition of the Earth's interior.

ZH: 地质勘探是发现矿藏和石油的重要手段。
EN: Geological exploration is an important means of discovering mineral deposits and oil.

ZH: 地质灾害频发，给当地居民带来了很多困扰。
EN: Frequent geological disasters have brought a lot of trouble to local residents.

ZH: 他是一名地质工程师，专门从事地下水资源的开发和利用。
EN: He is a geological engineer specializing in the development and utilization of groundwater resources.

ZH: 这座建筑的基础必须经过地质勘察才能确定。
EN: The foundation of this building must be determined through geological exploration.

