EN: Geological resources are an important foundation for the development of human society.

ZH: 这块石头的颜色和形状显示了其特殊的地质特征。
EN: The color and shape of this rock display its unique geological features.

ZH: 地质勘探为建设交通基础设施提供了重要依据。
EN: Geological exploration provides important basis for the construction of transportation infrastructure.

ZH: 他们在河流的两岸进行了地质调查，确保工程的安全性。
EN: They conducted geological surveys on both sides of the river to ensure the safety of the project.

ZH: 地质学家根据地层结构推断出了石油的储藏位置。
EN: Geologists inferred the location of oil reserves based on the geological structure.

ZH: 这里地质条件适合建设水电站。
EN: The geological conditions here are suitable for the construction of hydroelectric power stations.

ZH: 主要的地质构造是由地壳板块的运动形成的。
EN: The main geological structures are formed by the movement of the Earth's crustal plates.

ZH: 地质工作者在峡谷中发现了化石化石。
EN: Geological workers discovered fossilized fossils in the canyon.

ZH: 地质岩层的变化对地下水的流动产生了重要影响。
EN: The changes in geological strata have important impacts on the flow of groundwater.

ZH: 地质学家对这座活火山的喷发活动进行了监测。
EN: Geologists monitored the volcanic eruption activity of this active volcano.

